189
00:07:37,041 --> 00:07:38,918
AI! QUE DIABOS
HÁ DE ERRADO COM VOCÊ?

190
00:07:39,002 --> 00:07:40,211
CAM!

191
00:07:40,295 --> 00:07:41,796
BRIGA COMIGO!

192
00:07:43,298 --> 00:07:44,340
ZIG:
(GEMENDO DE DOR)

193
00:07:44,424 --> 00:07:46,176
MAYA:
